{"tid":2197493,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"驚方聲稱被捕人士沽空壹傳媒","createTime":"2020-09-10T15:50:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T16:33:21.000Z","uid":105567,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3e7266f2338194a416f0981a6575c08a24db730d","tid":2197493,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:50:20.000Z","msg":"簡單來說，「沽空」是指你在出售股票時，並無持有該股票，但對有關股票擁有一項即時可行使而無條件的售賣權利。然而，並非所有股票均可沽空。<br />\n<br />\n哪些證券可沽空？<br />\n<br />\n目前，只有被聯交所列為「可進行賣空的指定證券」才可進行沽空。<br />\n<br />\n可進行賣空的指定證券名單如下：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkex.com.hk/Services/Trading/Securities/Securities-Lists/Designated-Securities-Eligible-for-Short-Selling?sc_lang=zh-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkex.com.hk%2FServices%2FTrading%2FSecurities%2FSecurities-Lists%2FDesignated-Securities-Eligible-for-Short-Selling%3Fsc_lang%3Dzh-HK&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FJ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=dab63f52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkex.com.hk/Services/Trading/Securities/Securities-Lists/Designated-Securities-Eligible-for-Short-Selling?sc_lang=zh-HK</a><br />\n<br />\n#你都識人哋低買高賣<br />\n#有貨嘅情況下賣又邊係沽空<br />\n#睇錢家有道學下理財知識先啦 顯示較少內容<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jbOjwxc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjbOjwxc.jpg&h=94fd3036&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6757b97ad9dc75953a1a631dbe9fb6f5bbd35787","tid":2197493,"uid":357710,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3e7266f2338194a416f0981a6575c08a24db730d","tid":2197493,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:50:20.000Z","msg":"簡單來說，「沽空」是指你在出售股票時，並無持有該股票，但對有關股票擁有一項即時可行使而無條件的售賣權利。然而，並非所有股票均可沽空。<br />\n<br />\n哪些證券可沽空？<br />\n<br />\n目前，只有被聯交所列為「可進行賣空的指定證券」才可進行沽空。<br />\n<br />\n可進行賣空的指定證券名單如下：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkex.com.hk/Services/Trading/Securities/Securities-Lists/Designated-Securities-Eligible-for-Short-Selling?sc_lang=zh-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?