mbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjbOjwxc.jpg&h=94fd3036&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T16:00:28.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">他們從高頻率買賣交易過程囤積一定數量的低價購入股票。</span>當他們誘導一般投資者在高位買入股票後，他們便順勢在高位沽空，讓股票的價格大幅下跌。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣解是高位<span class=\"red\">有貨沽空</span> &quot;囤積一定數量的低價購入股票&quot;<br />\n<br />\n如果你是講<span class=\"red\">無貨沽空</span>，文章會變成這樣:<br />\n他們便順勢在高位沽空，讓股票的價格大幅下跌，然後在T+2交易期內低位補回沽空股票作交易。"},{"pid":"715041c242d0b8f1d24c208a9a7e3526376a4533","tid":2197493,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T16:31:22.000Z","msg":"係都捉佢「跟」據啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d38819c38d77e401e95e0f14a6994080ae48b754","tid":2197493,"uid":370897,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f1bfe6ae0afad09c75043845e1531912f1e7b71","tid":2197493,"uid":357710,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"3e7266f2338194a416f0981a6575c08a24db730d","tid":2197493,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T15:50:20.000Z","msg":"簡單來說，「沽空」是指你在出售股票時，並無持有該股票，但對有關股票擁有一項即時可行使而無條件的售賣權利。然而，並非所有股票均可沽空。<br />\n<br />\n哪些證券可沽空？<br />\n<br />\n目前，只有被聯交所列為「可進行賣空的指定證券」才可進行沽空。<br />\n<br />\n可進行賣空的指定證券名單如下：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkex.com.hk/Services/Trading/Securities/Securities-Lists/Designated-Securities-Eligible-for-Short-Selling?sc_lang=zh-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkex.com.hk%2FServices%2FTrading%2FSecurities%2FSecurities-Lists%2FDesignated-Securities-Eligible-for-Short-Selling%3Fsc_lang%3Dzh-HK&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FJ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=dab63f52\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkex.com.hk/Services/Trading/Securities/Securities-Lists/Designated-Securities-Eligible-for-Short-Selling?sc_lang=zh-HK</a><br />\n<br />\n#你都識人哋低買高賣<br />\n#有貨嘅情況下賣又邊係沽空<br />\n#睇錢家有道學下理財知識先啦 顯示較少內容<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jbOjwxc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https: